data.description: 2.7% VA ASSUMABLE LOAN!! Back on the market!! Buyer’s received orders somewhere else. This gorgeous home is located in the Los Suenos community. The 4 bedroom 2 bath that is open with a split design features luxury wood look tile flooring, quartz countertops, upgraded cabinets, doubly vanity, garden tub, a separate shower, kitchen island and much more! You are only minutes from the beaches, schools, shopping and Pensacola NAS.
